  <summary date="2021-10-28T20:03:14Z" status="Introduced in House">Safe Skies Act of 2021

This bill directs the Department of Transportation (DOT) to modify a specified DOT final rule relating to flight crew member duty and rest requirements so that the requirements under that rule apply to all-cargo flight crew members to the same extent they apply to air passenger flight crew members.</summary>
